name: MALAMADA
description:
Section of photographs that give new meaning to daily oppressions in the female black body. On the choker  we have written in Brazilian Portuguese the offenses that repress  women. Brazil is among the biggest countries that commit violence against women. Feminicide is the murder of a woman for the condition of being a woman. Their most common motivations are hatred, contempt or a feeling of loss of control and ownership over women.
My Instagram: (@gabugusmão) (@gabunira)
